{"tid":2363570,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦ssd求救，啟用時間100%","createTime":"2021-01-12T09:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T03:22:22.000Z","uid":100088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"611c8b6db6ced3c32139fca835891eeaacbd79c2","tid":2363570,"uid":100088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"部腦有2個ssd, C 同 Z drive<br />\nZ新買既想裝game用，但最近開始好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前2日熄機前仲好地地，但最近開機上下網睇下片都唔覺有野。<br />\n係想開game打機既時候，所有野都慢過平時100倍<br />\n<br />\n幾百mb既象素獨立遊戲都可能仲開到（但明顯感覺到載入慢左）<br />\n開始試d 大型小小既如Xcom2，淨係開個launcher 佢個啟用時間已經爆到上100%，長升唔跌，放係到load 30分鐘到沒有回應都無進展<br />\n（唔知寫入速度關唔關事，但長期都係0-50kb咁彈一彈）<br />\n<br />\n但一用task manager熄左佢就即刻番番0%<br />\n而task manager到望到隻遊戲其實只係用緊0.1mb，但個磁碟使用率就爆到上33%, 而且電源用量會話「非常高」<br />\n<br />\n但有時部腦開耐左，可能大半日啦，佢又會慢慢可以用得番，打到機，雖然都係反應慢左小小，但都叫郁到<br />\n<br />\nPs: 試過隨便係C drive到開d以前裝落既遊戲，都係好快開到，啟用時間都係10-30%左右<br />\n<br />\n有無大師可以解答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaROB6q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaROB6q.png&h=be483b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23Cx3MH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23Cx3MH.png&h=8d556fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/howGcFi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhowGcFi.png&h=497938cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5b4e82474ae333dd81d1bf13129a9ba3e57edbc","tid":2363570,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"就咁過file速度正常？"},{"pid":"ddb2f30424593da52300ab33f06382cad93b0b55","tid":2363570,"uid":103948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"53e60cc507b5ac33623d5d14831d2a56fad4c76e","tid":2363570,"uid":372390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"SSD Controller 過熱？"},{"pid":"dda3ac1cf43d7238571e7eb85ada2dff54fde7dc","tid":2363570,"uid":100088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53e60cc507b5ac33623d5d14831d2a56fad4c76e","tid":2363570,"uid":372390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"SSD Controller 過熱？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"邊到睇？<br />\n<br />\n用samsung個管理器睇同做test<br />\n一切正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37801b26b873c988c5ee82eab7d2f538660bec12","tid":2363570,"uid":100088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5b4e82474ae333dd81d1bf13129a9ba3e57edbc","tid":2363570,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"就咁過file速度正常？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"今晚有緣再試，而家開機直頭話「自動修復」入左去個黑畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a5e1a1f49408e12e651478c79989337f9433a9","tid":2363570,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"壞咗 攞去保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f0ee60e6ba6a7a9467492e5e5fd6e252cdbf4c","tid":2363570,"uid":306444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"CrystalDiskInfo用左未<img s